  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales & Marketing Executive (Outdoor)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li><p>Actively promote and sell company's all products/services to new customers (BCO /Direct Shippers) through outdoor sales visits.</p></li><li><p>Identify and develop new business opportunities to achieve sales targets.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong customer relationships, ensuring high levels of customer satisfaction.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and deliver sales presentations, proposals, and quotations to clients.</p></li><li><p>Conduct market research to stay updated on industry trends, competitor activities, and customer needs.</p></li><li><p>Negotiate and close sales deals in line with company policies.</p></li><li><p>Provide regular sales reports, forecasts, and updates to management.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with internal teams (marketing, operations, customer service) to ensure smooth order execution.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Educational Qualifications as per requirements.</p></li><li><p>Proven experience in outdoor sales, business development, or similar role.</p></li><li><p>Strong communication, negotiation, and interpersonal skills.</p></li><li><p>Goal-oriented, self-motivated, and able to work independently with minimal supervision.</p></li><li><p>Good presentation and persuasive selling skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to handle pressure and achieve sales targets.</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, energetic, and Team oriented/Team Player.</p></li><li><p>Possess a valid driving license will be added advantage/Merit.</p></li><li><p>Must possess own vehicle</p></li></ul>",
